{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-04015/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-04015"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:40:15"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["extreme close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["high"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}}],"summary":{"none":["The name \"Alma\" sewn in pink thread on a piece of fabric."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-04015","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-04015"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1/b999c193-7442-4f2d-a6b6-4fdcd0a1cee4","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:05:21.685Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The “phantom thread” of Alma’s dress is her name, embroidered into the fabric. Her name has become an emblem of their passion since their initial encounter at the restaurant, and here, Reynolds reproduces it, much as Cyril did so when taking Alma’s measurements during Reynolds and Alma’s first date.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:726.1372812920592,330.04037685060587,545.2489905787348,452.2207267833108"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1/ad2be72e-4b2f-4a83-adc7-1cf8a3d76dc7","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:05:43.020Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>As Reynolds sews her name into the seam of the dress, he eclipses it with the fabric he prizes, subsuming her personal identity, her very selfhood, into his art. Her individuality becomes merely another part of his craft, that he can shape and display however he wants.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04015/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:736.4737550471066,109.09825033647388,258.4118438761777,197.68506056527593"}}}]}]}]}